Ifeoma Iphie Aggrey-Fynn (8 June n’afọ 1980 - 2 June n’afọ 2015), nke a maara dị ka Iphie, bụ onye mgbasa ozi Ghana na Naijiria, onye edemede na onye na-ekwu okwu n'ihu ọha.
Ọrụ Aggrey-Fynn na mgbasa ozi malitere dị ka onye na-egosi TV na 2003
Mgbe ọ banyere na Silverbird Communications n'afọ 2009, e bufere ya ịrụ ọrụ na Rhythm 95.7 FM na Silverbird Television na Awka
N'ebe ahụ, ọ kwadoro ihe ngosi redio na TV gụnyere Rhythm & Soul, Gospel Vibes na E-Merge tupu ọ kwaga Rhythm 93.7 FM Port Harcourt.
Ọ bụkwa onye nnabata ugboro atọ nke Miss Niger Delta beauty pageant
